product_type                  gravity_field
earth_gravity_constant        3.986004415E+14
radius                        6.378136300E+06
max_degree                    240
errors                        calibrated
norm                          fully_normalized
tide_system                   zero_tide
  
key    L    M         C                  S               sigma C      sigma S
